    <!-- Decay system -->
    <div class="border-y border-green-700/40 py-3 my-4">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-green-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Decay rate</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-xs text-green-600 mb-2">
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-3"><span>Last edition</span><span class="text-green-300 font-bold">100%</span></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-3"><span>2 editions ago</span><span class="text-yellow-400/80 font-bold">50%</span></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-3"><span>3 editions ago</span><span class="text-orange-400/80 font-bold">25%</span></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-3"><span>4 editions ago</span><span class="text-red-400/80 font-bold">10%</span></div>
        <div class="flex justify-between gap-3"><span>Older than 4</span><span class="text-gray-500 font-bold">0%</span></div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-green-200 text-sm mb-2">
        <strong>Purpose:</strong> Recent activity weighs more than old one. This keeps rankings dynamic and rewards current participation. The purpose of doing this is to simulate realistic consistency.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-green-500 mt-2">
        <strong>Example:</strong> 10 pts from last edition = 10 pts. The same 10 pts from two editions ago = 5 pts (50% decay).
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional info -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-green-300 font-medium text-center mb-4">
        Points can be earned in all categories <strong>until the deadline</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-green-300 mb-1">
        The <strong>first 24 Forestian teams to sign up</strong> qualify directly for the <strong>Group Stage</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-green-400">
        The <strong>ranking</strong> does not determine classification, but rather the <strong>pot</strong> in which each team will be placed during the draw.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-green-500 mt-1">
        Teams that sign up after the first 24 will be placed in the <strong>last pot and may have to play playoffs</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
